        <ul>
          <li>The images should be as close as possible to the question iamge</li>
          <li>Image could be in rotated formate than the question image</li>
          <li>The image should have good color balance.  (i.e. not tinted)</li>
          <li>The image may appear in different ligting condition than the question image</li>
          <li>The image could be in different zoom level than the question image</li>
